::Shredder::

Shredder spins around as he hears a phrase in his mind, nearly firing his 
guns as he sees Wildfire. He growls to himself. There were two predacons 
present, probably a bit tough for him to handle. On the other hand, there 
were two Maximal somewhere up north.....

He nearly jumps as he recieves the transmission from Magmatron, thinking for 
a sec that it might once again be a message in his mind.

"They're both preds," he replies into his comm-link, "I got it taken care of 
though."

Shredder looks from Wildfire to Lobstruck, deactivating his comm. "I am a 
Predacon as well. There are two Maximal signatures up north, I am going to 
slag them. You're welcome to help."

With that, he turns back around, once again heading toward Lunarpine and 
Shadow Wing.
